## 16. Monetisation

> *Monetisation must never gate social mechanics, provide combat advantage, or allow real money to substitute for in-game economic activity.*

| Item | Notes |
|---|---|
| Cosmetic Camps | Visual themes for your camp — aesthetic only |
| Survivor Portraits | Custom artwork for survivor characters |
| Caravan Name Tokens | Additional custom name slots (1 free rename per 30 days) |
| Season Pass | Narrative expansion packs with new Encounter stories and Trader types |
| Memorialisation | Permanent epitaph for a fallen high-level survivor in the Lost Caravan log |
| **NOT for sale** | Combat stats, chain speed, market priority, death protection, level restoration, Cipher, Valuables, or any in-game currency or asset |

