## 17. MVP Scope

### 17.1 Must Have (Launch)

- BLE proximity detection, background mode, iOS and Android
- Chain formation and length tracking up to 8 links
- Tier 1–4 chain bonuses
- 3 entity types: hostile, neutral, trader — opt-in flags and server bots
- Asynchronous combat resolution with 2-minute commitment window
- Defensive instakill mechanic — level gap quadratic curve, 35% cap
- Hardcore death: level reset, loot drop, 60-second killer priority window
- Loot tiers Common through Legendary; Bound item system
- Single primary currency (Valuables) with configurable backing
- Global order book with 5% auto-match rule
- Derivative instruments: futures and options on resource commodities
- Cipher system: per-syndicate closed ledger, leader visibility, rate-limited minting
- Cipher Bridge: bilateral syndicate exchange agreements
- 5 survivor roles, no skill trees at launch
- Basic political system: elections, tariffs, embargos
- Reputation and Infamy systems with access thresholds
- Anonymous identity — generated caravan names, no GPS, no real identity

### 17.2 Post-Launch

- Survivor skill trees and level progression depth
- Full treasury management tools for nation leaders
- Currency collapse and recovery mechanics (full implementation)
- Bounty system for syndicates
- Protection racket enforcement mechanics
- NPC syndicate lore expansion and permanent fixture events
- Faction/nation discovery — how new nations form from chain clusters
- Seasonal economic events: supply shocks, world events affecting commodity prices
- Lost Caravan memorialisation — public death records visible to all players

